mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From the Floor", "On the Record and Record Report", "Square Dance Date Book", "Square Dance Date Book", "As I See It", "Let's Double the Dancers, 1963 Recruiting Program", "Overseas Dateline", "The Dancer's Walkthru", "Plan a Dancer Census", "Ladies on the Square", "Style Series: Some Theory, Subject: Cross Trail", "Round the Outside Ring", "Workshop", "Square Dance Indoctrination Handbook", "Caller of the Month: Gerry Hawley", "Paging the Roundancers: Joe Boykin", and "Experimental Lab: Ends Cross Over - Centers Swing".
